eNCA's Barry Bateman has more on this story. Courtesy #DStv403 PRETORIA - While Tshwane Municipality forges ahead with its disconnection blitz against defaulting consumers, some have hit back, saying they’re being unfairly and unlawfully treated. They've turned to the courts - and won but the municipality insists it will continue. eNCA's Barry Bateman has more on this story in the video above.